    <para styleclass="Normal"><tab /><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">x - The x coordinate of the cursor in chart coordinates</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><tab /><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">y - The y coordinate of the cursor in chart coordinates</text></para>
